manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: JIMEIQI Accordion File Organizer This portfolio is a combination of clipboard and folder. Despite its compact 13"x 9.6" size, this folder offers generous storage. As a clipboard, it’s firm, sturdy, and comfortable to write on. Yet, it is better than a standard clipboard because the pages are protected, and the cover provides privacy. As a folder, it has different types of including a storage bag, which efficiently keeps notes, papers, tags, mail, receipts and business cards organized in one place. This folder is sure to make any home, office, school, or travel scenario more organized and efficient.

Convenient Storage Bag Ensure your must-haves stay safely stowed away in this roomy storage bag. It's the perfect solution for keeping your essentials secure and within easy reach. Elevate your organizational prowess with this spacious storage companion. High Quality Notebook This legal pad provides a tidy and accessible area for writing. It's an ideal choice for scribbling job interview queries, recording boardroom discussions, or capturing bursts of creativity for your next major marketing initiative. Moreover, it's highly useful for home improvement plans, managing tasks, or taking notes during classroom lectures at university Upgraded Snap Button Say goodbye to fumbling and frustration. Our enhanced snap button ensures that opening and closing your folder is a breeze, providing quick access to your documents. It's all about convenience and efficiency. Make your daily routine smoother and more hassle-free with our user-friendly snap button. Convenient Storage Bag High Quality Notebook Upgraded Snap Button

Q1: What compartments are included in this file folder for organization? A1: This file folder boasts 6 individual pockets, 1 notebook paper pocket, 1legal pads,1 storage bag, and 1 main pocket, offering a variety of storage compartments for efficient organization. Q2: Can you describe the benefits of the upgraded snap button? A2: The upgraded snap button ensures effortless access, making it easier to open and close the folder, allowing for quick retrieval of your items. Q3: Is this file folder made from materials? A3: Yes, this file folder is crafted from PP material, which is acid-free, PVC-free, and of archival quality. This ensures that your documents are well-protected and durable. Q4: What is the size of this file organizer, and what can it hold? A4: The compact size of this accordion file organizer is 13"x 9.6". Despite its size, it offers ample space for storing letter/A4 files, receipts, cards, USB drives, pens, passports, and more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I am pleased to have found this slim organizer. I bought it with the intention of using it at my kids IEP meeting. It easily holds the documents I need to bring with me and provides the space for me to also take notes during the meeting. It would be ideal to have a note pad with more pages, but the small note pad provided is not a deal breaker and is easily replaced.
